Text.string: I'm a disfigured freak of robo-nature! Help!
Recruit! You have to help me! I... I LOST MY ANTENNA! Wagahghhghghh!
Just jump over it and hit crouch!
Nice butt power!
No! NO WIRE HANGERS!
Don't touch my DELICATES!
Ooh! Watch out for all that scary electricity! There's gotta be a way to shut it off!
Watch your feet! You DON'T want to step in that.
If you don't shut off the electricity, I'll never get my antenna!
I'm sure there's some way to cut the power, but you clearly haven't figured it out yet!
Just shoot the switch to turn off the electricity!
Now get me that thing!
Go on! Climb up there!
Will you stop crying if I say I'll help?
Aww. It's okay, little buddy. I can help.
I know your pain, little friend. I will assist you.
This is an opportunity, boyo! I can help you freshen up yer look!
You know you can climb up there, right?
I know you can climb! Even though you don't have my powerful robot clamps! You can do it!
What a spread! I can't decide! You've gotta choose for me, recruit! But beware—you hold my very aesthetic in your hands! Now: complete me!
Is this the one?
Does that look right?
How do you like this one?
This one? Are ya sure?
Let's try something else!
All right, back to the drawing board.
Your call! I trust you completely!
You wanna try out another one?
Well?! How do I look?
It's, uh. It's great. You're great. Whatever.
Oh, you. You... look just, just splendid.
It completes you.
Lookin' snazzy, boyo. The ladybots are gonna love it.
Please help me!
Great! Now I outrank you AND outclass you! Next to me, you're looking kinda shabby—you might wanna find a Quick-Change and spruce up your look, too!
There MUST be something down there! See if you can open that floor-door somehow!
Ooooh! A spork might look nice! I'll rinse it off later.
Ooh, a coat hanger? Yeah, that could give me sort of a... rustic vibe. No, a rusty vibe.
That looks just like my old antenna. Can't go wrong with a Claptrap Classic™!
Ooh, that psycho is sporting a GREAT HAT! I want it! Get it for me, recruit! Just go talk to him! He seems reasonable enough.
Shiny! That hat would make me the talk of the town! Those snooty aristocrats couldn't kick me out of their fancy galas anymore!
Hey! I bet there's something in there we could use! Check it out!
Yes! I'm gonna be bigger and badder than ever! But this is an important fashion decision. Bring me replacement antenna options, recruit! OPTIONS, I say!
With an umbrella like that, I'd look like a fancy cocktail! Everyone's gonna want a sip of this guy!
We've got some good options, recruit! Return to me and we'll try 'em out!
Go forth! Even though finding me a new antenna is vitally important, you can do this mission on the SIDE. And you'll probably want to get a vehicle for this one!
Jump at the edge of things and jump again to mantle up onto it! Do we have to take you back to basic training?
Now destroy that ECHOtransponder!
And pick up the antenna!
There's gotta be a way to get that door open!
Greetings, chum! How does the day find you?
Are you one of these COV lunatics or what?
I'm keeping an eye on you. No sudden movements.
Your cordial greeting has me uneasy for some reason.
Well, lookit you, a proper gentleman and everything. What's the catch?
Fear not, friend! I am keeping the voices at bay with this mighty cap atop my head!
Cool. Cool. Super cool. So can I have that hat or...?
Riiight. Well, I'm gonna need that hat.
I require that metal headpiece.
I'm gonna need that “mighty cap”.
Oh, no no. I couldn't possibly part with it. Not right now. You'll have to destroy the mind control transmission dishes first! They're beaming voices into my brain!
You heard the man! Destroy those transmission dishes! I need that hat!
Ahh, I can feel the mind control releasing its hold!
Yes! Keep destroying the dishes so that I can finally be free of the voices!
Haha! Now, I am free!
Yes! Free of those horrible CALMING VOICES! I can FINALLY BE THE SKIN CUPCAKE! RRRGGAAAAAAGH!
Maybe you can get up high and slam down on it?
Well, he's dead! Now pick up that hat!
You'll have to get under that thing somehow.
How low can you go? Pretty low, if you ask me.
You can make it through! I believe in you, just... stealth slide!
Just sprint at the opening and hit crouch! It's not that hard.
Can't get me in here, Vault Thief!
Ha, having some trouble?
You'll never get in here!
Neener neener, Vault Thief! Just give up!
That umbrella would come in handy when it rains on Pandora never!
That's a COV ECHOtransponder! Who knows what kind of nefarious broadcasts they might be sending with that thing! Climb up there and destroy it!
Get real high and jump-crouch to tap into your inner strength!
